を「栗」に見立てています。<br />\n出典：DRAGONBALL FOREVER(ﾄﾞﾗｺﾞﾝﾎﾞｰﾙ ﾌｫｰｴﾊﾞｰ) <br />\n<br />\nFrom Yahoo JP<br />\n<br />\n大約係講緊 鳥山明設計完無限呢個角色後 因應無限個樣而求其改個名 因為佢無諗住繼續畫無限 所以求其改<br />\n<br />\n而佢之後改佢個女個名既時候 定名為マーロン（マロン係歐洲栗子) <br />\n而咁岩クリリン個クリ漢字係栗(くり) 先至有人會同聯想到栗子 但其實無限唔關栗子事 係鳩改而已"},{"pid":"584a3958b706f14f1b97d8d8c7a8f29c0168e10f","tid":602550,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:19:55.000Z","msg":"無限既潛能"},{"pid":"61adfbf0f27f28774710479e90442704a4438c8d","tid":602550,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584a3958b706f14f1b97d8d8c7a8f29c0168e10f","tid":602550,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:19:55.000Z","msg":"無限既潛能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"有潛能？"},{"pid":"5125efa249d015e2bec823ebf9c8839efe279130","tid":602550,"uid":162157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"問下無限老母"},{"pid":"54a6404413a49119f4aef9dc51fdc9d11d74726e","tid":602550,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61adfbf0f27f28774710479e90442704a4438c8d","tid":602550,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584a3958b706f14f1b97d8d8c7a8f29c0168e10f","tid":602550,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:19:55.000Z","msg":"無限既潛能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"有潛能？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"溝女個方面"},{"pid":"34333059c30dba2806e1e073db9a32aaf22568b2","tid":602550,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無限既潛能</blockquote><br />\n有潛能？</blockquote><br />\n氣圓斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916485ae4473dad7d57f521736248482fae8876e","tid":602550,"uid":31961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>悟空的朋友<br />\n<br />\n<span 